quran[8{c,v,t}:
2,238,Haafizoo 'alas salawaati was Salaatil Wustaa wa qoomoo lillaahi qaaniteen
2,239,Fa in khiftum farijaalan aw rukbaanan fa izaaa amintum fazkurul laaha kamaa 'allamakum maa lam takoonoo ta'lamoon
2,240,Wallazeena yutawaf fawna minkum wa yazaroona azwaajanw wasiyyatal li azwaajihim mataa'an ilal hawlighaira ikhraaj; fa in kharajna falaa junaaha 'alaikum fee maa fa'alna junaaha 'alaikum fee maa fa'alna feee anfusihinna mim ma'roof; wallaahu Azeezun Hakeem
2,241,Wa lilmutallaqaati mataa'um bilma'roofi haqqan 'alal muttaqeen
2,242,Kazaalika yubaiyinul laahu lakum aayaatihee la'allakum ta'qiloon�(section 31)
2,243,Alam tara ilal lazeena kharajoo min diyaarihim wa hum uloofun hazaral mawti faqaaala lahumul laahu mootoo summa ahyaahum; innal laaha lazoo fadlin 'alannaasi wa laakinna aksarannaasi laa yashkuroon
2,244,Wa qaatiloo fee sabeelil laahi wa'lamooo annal laaha Samee'un 'Aleem
2,245,Man zal lazee yuqridul laaha qardan hasanan fayudaa 'ifahoo lahoo ad'aafan kaseerah; wallaahu yaqbidu wa yabsut(u) wa ilaihi turja'oon
